      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">获取&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\">CommandBars</b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;集合中的&nbsp;</span><b style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\">CommandBar</b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">&nbsp;对象。只读。</span> </p>",
