    {
      "name": "LargeButtons",
      "summary": "<p>\n</p><p>\n</p><p></p><table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th><img/>注释</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>在某些 WPS Office应用程序中，CommandBar \n已被新的功能区用户界面取代。有关详细信息，请在帮助中搜索关键字“功能区”。</td></tr></tbody></table>",
      "description": "<p>\n</p><p></p><p>如果显示的工具栏按钮比常规尺寸要大，则为 <b>True</b>。可读写。</p>",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code class=\"JavaScript\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//本示例在所有命令栏上的工具栏按钮的显示大小间切换。  </span>\n<span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n</span>{\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(Application.CommandBars.LargeButtons)\n    {\n        Application.CommandBars.LargeButtons = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    }\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>\n    {\n        Application.CommandBars.LargeButtons = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [],
      "type": "",
      "value": "",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
